      "role": "user",
      "content": "i get the balance thing but it feels like a bit of an easy way out lol. if you had to pick one to be the absolute foundation of a healthy country, which would it be? like, can you actually have a stable society if the debt is spiraling, even if the safety nets are good? or is the debt just a bogeyman used to justify cutting help for people?",
